Hello Turo travelers! I'm your dedicated Turo Host and I'm here to ensure that your rental experience is extraordinary. With a passion for cars and a commitment to providing top-notch service, I've embraced Turo as a platform that allows me to share my love for automobiles with fellow enthusiasts and explorers.

I believe in delivering an exceptional experience. From the moment you book one of my cars, my goal is to make your journey as smooth and enjoyable as possible. I maintain my vehicles with care and ensure they're clean and in top-notch condition. Punctuality, timely communication, and a willingness to go the extra mile are the cornerstones of my hosting approach.

Connect With Me:
If you have any questions, special requests, or simply want to discuss your travel plans, please reach out to me on the Turo message box or at 301-919-0642
 I'm eager to connect with travelers, share insights, and ensure your Turo experience is nothing short of extraordinary.

I'm a happy husband and very proud dad of 2 wonderful kids.  I volunteer in the community with sports and boy scouts as a way of giving back and contributing to others.

I've traveled ALOT around the world and have seen the disasters that happen so often with renting cars.  I'm very committed to providing a great experience all around.

Thank you for considering booking one of my vehicles, and my promise to you is a positive Turo experience.  I understand that means different things to different guests, and I'm committed to that personalized service.

Safe travels!
-Tony
